    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Narrow, shallow canoes common in East Africa, made of hollowed-out tree trunks and equipped with outriggers of both sides.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
